===Etymology===
From {{inh|en|enm|comly}}, {{m|enm|cumly}}, {{m|enm|cumlich}}, from {{inh|en|ang|cymlīċ}}, {{m|ang|cȳmlīċ}} (compare {{cog|ang|cȳme|t=fine, exquisite}}, from {{cog|gem-pro|*kūmiz||delicate}}), from {{inh|en|gem-pro|*kūmalīkaz|t=pitiful, dear}}. Cognate with {{cog|dum|komlick}}, {{m|dum|komelick}}, {{cog|gmh|komelīh}}, {{m|gmh|gomelīh}}.

